{"tid":1730014,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港公開羽毛球錦標賽　港隊李卓耀奪男單冠軍","createTime":"2019-11-17T12:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T16:22:57.000Z","uid":208765,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea82b10814c126b06927374f770acc8826283ad","tid":1730014,"uid":208765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:04:19.000Z","msg":"香港公開羽毛球錦標賽，港隊男單代表李卓耀，在決賽反勝印尼球手金廷局數2:1，贏得冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n李卓耀首局受制於對手速度及網前球，未能發揮水準，先輸16:21。第二局李卓耀調整後，搶回不少攻勢，對手失誤亦增加，李卓耀以21:10追回一局，雙方要以決勝局分勝負。<br />\n<br />\n李卓耀在決勝局大部分時間都領先，但金廷後來居上，先取得場點，李卓耀在全場觀眾大力打氣下，頂著壓力追成20:20，並反超前21:20，金廷之後撲網，被球證判犯規，令李卓耀以22:20，結束這場打了77分鐘的賽事，取得冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492793-20191117.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492793-20191117.htm&d=sw6tlk2lcpT%2BYldK84vytBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=d7b378fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492793-20191117.htm&h=893509cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492793-20191117.htm</a>"},{"pid":"95a260b8108e66fc711f535b2aefc13fe6756078","tid":1730014,"uid":208765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37de2d1fef59ddf27eb3b6b9c6a19d5b98983ad","tid":1730014,"uid":162477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:05:29.000Z","msg":"好厲害！"},{"pid":"2359db4a52958206e5f4a94fd683dff7e950480c","tid":1730014,"uid":208765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803173eca574eb4569